= Skeletor

Skeleton Application which contains an example configuration for qcore and qcms gems.

See the "Wiki":http://github.com/krisleech/skeletor/wiki for more information.

== Configure

database.yml
sitemap.yml
settings.yml

== Bootstrap

rake qwerty:bootstrap

== Deployment

You need to create /public/uploads folder for FCKeditor image uploads

== Configure Development Tools (optional)

=== XRefresh

rake xrefresh:configure
rake xrefresh:run

Enable xrefresh panel in Firebug

== Notes

Versioning schema: http://semver.org